      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve totally babied it, keeping it garaged and pampered since day one. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it's a total dream to drive! I'm happy to answer any questions or have you come by to see it for yourself. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your new favorite ride!",
