      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing service. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, precise gates, transferring power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original suspension kinematics with zero bushing deflection, and the exterior finish remains in showroom condition. This is a rare opportunity to own a high-revving, naturally aspirated icon that has been maintained to the highest technical standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
